00:23:46.660 --> 00:23:47.650 align:middle line:84%
running, as a matter of fact.
LINDA BENDER: Yes.

00:23:47.650 --> 00:23:49.216 align:middle line:84%
REGINA MEREDITH: Michael
Telligner, David Eich.

00:23:49.216 --> 00:23:49.970 align:middle line:90%
LINDA BENDER: Yes.

00:23:49.970 --> 00:23:52.660 align:middle line:84%
REGINA MEREDITH: These are
great, great supporters

00:23:52.660 --> 00:23:54.340 align:middle line:90%
of Credo Mutwa's work as well.

00:23:54.340 --> 00:23:55.260 align:middle line:90%
LINDA BENDER: Yes.

00:23:55.260 --> 00:23:57.190 align:middle line:84%
But your connection
with him is specifically

00:23:57.190 --> 00:23:59.611 align:middle line:84%
having to do with the sacredness
of the animal kingdom.

00:23:59.611 --> 00:24:00.310 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:02.940 align:middle line:84%
And I am so very
grateful, because I

00:24:02.940 --> 00:24:06.970 align:middle line:84%
was able to spend a week
with Credo at his home

00:24:06.970 --> 00:24:11.690 align:middle line:84%
and learn from him, and
hear his lifelong stories.

00:24:11.690 --> 00:24:13.030 align:middle line:90%
He's about 94 now.

00:24:13.030 --> 00:24:13.730 align:middle line:90%
REGINA MEREDITH: Yes.

00:24:13.730 --> 00:24:15.885 align:middle line:84%
Except if there are young
women around, he says he's 89.

00:24:15.885 --> 00:24:16.934 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:24:16.934 --> 00:24:18.110 align:middle line:90%
[INAUDIBLE].

00:24:18.110 --> 00:24:22.580 align:middle line:84%
But he's a wonderful
source of shamanic wisdom.

00:24:22.580 --> 00:24:24.910 align:middle line:84%
Well, he's the record keeper
for the Zulu tradition right?

00:24:24.910 --> 00:24:25.950 align:middle line:90%
He truly is.

00:24:25.950 --> 00:24:30.090 align:middle line:84%
But he's also the keeper of
the tragedy and the pain--

00:24:30.090 --> 00:24:30.890 align:middle line:90%
REGINA MEREDITH: Yes.

00:24:30.890 --> 00:24:33.210 align:middle line:84%
---of the animals
and the people.

00:24:33.210 --> 00:24:37.735 align:middle line:84%
And so his stories are
sometimes heartbreaking.

00:24:37.735 --> 00:24:42.780 align:middle line:84%
But I went there specifically
to deepen my sacred connection.

00:24:42.780 --> 00:24:46.721 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that I could learn
more, and more, and more.

00:24:46.721 --> 00:24:47.420 align:middle line:90%
And that he--

00:24:47.420 --> 00:24:48.820 align:middle line:84%
And what did you
take away from there

00:24:48.820 --> 00:24:50.780 align:middle line:90%
that was the most profound?

00:24:50.780 --> 00:24:53.390 align:middle line:90%
He was so inspiring.

00:24:53.390 --> 00:24:56.040 align:middle line:84%
And he said all
of us have a gift.

00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:59.660 align:middle line:84%
All of us have our unique
gift, be it helping animals

00:24:59.660 --> 00:25:01.965 align:middle line:90%
or helping the poor with AIDS.

00:25:01.965 --> 00:25:06.750 align:middle line:84%
He was particularly
active in helping AIDS.

00:25:06.750 --> 00:25:10.590 align:middle line:84%
We must take that
gift very seriously.

00:25:10.590 --> 00:25:13.030 align:middle line:90%
And that becomes our mission.

00:25:13.030 --> 00:25:16.790 align:middle line:90%
That becomes our life.

00:25:16.790 --> 00:25:20.730 align:middle line:84%
We become the warriors,
and a warrior never, ever,

00:25:20.730 --> 00:25:23.536 align:middle line:90%
ever deviates from that path.

00:25:23.536 --> 00:25:24.530 align:middle line:90%
REGINA MEREDITH: Yes.

00:25:24.530 --> 00:25:26.410 align:middle line:90%
We go on, and we go on.

00:25:26.410 --> 00:25:28.840 align:middle line:84%
And we go on not because
we're winning a battle,

00:25:28.840 --> 00:25:32.350 align:middle line:84%
but because we
cannot do otherwise.

00:25:32.350 --> 00:25:33.110 align:middle line:90%
That's beautiful.

00:25:33.110 --> 00:25:34.550 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:25:34.550 --> 00:25:37.740 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to ask you a little
bit ago if you wouldn't mind

00:25:37.740 --> 00:25:39.800 align:middle line:84%
sharing a couple of
those really deep,

00:25:39.800 --> 00:25:42.720 align:middle line:84%
connective experiences
you had with the elephants

00:25:42.720 --> 00:25:44.143 align:middle line:90%
you were referring to.

00:25:44.143 --> 00:25:46.390 align:middle line:90%
Yes, my elephants.

00:25:46.390 --> 00:25:50.150 align:middle line:84%
There was one
particular elephant

00:25:50.150 --> 00:25:55.820 align:middle line:84%
that I visited who
was with one other--

00:25:55.820 --> 00:25:57.860 align:middle line:90%
there were two male elephants.

00:25:57.860 --> 00:26:00.640 align:middle line:84%
This particular elephant
