00:56:22.010 --> 00:56:23.740 align:middle line:90%
Rupert doesn't endorse.

00:56:23.740 --> 00:56:25.270 align:middle line:84%
But it just shows the
power of your work.

00:56:25.270 --> 00:56:25.970 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:25.970 --> 00:56:28.500 align:middle line:84%
And he's done that beautiful
work with animals himself.

00:56:28.500 --> 00:56:29.200 align:middle line:90%
LINDA BENDER: Yes.

