Yes, sure.

00:56:35.630 --> 00:56:38.961 align:middle line:84%
Rupert Sheldrake is definitely
one of my all-time heroes.

00:56:38.961 --> 00:56:39.660 align:middle line:90%
REGINA MEREDITH: Yes.

